    p Sankalan, the annual technical festival of Department of Computer Science is the largest of its kind in northern India. It was conceived in 2005 with the aim of encouraging technology enthusiasts to showcase their intelligence and inventiveness through a wide array of technical and non technical events that promise to educate and inspire.
